Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{Opening}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.25,0:00:26.21,Karaoke,,0,0,0,,ashita he tsuzuku sakamichi no tochuu de
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.55,0:00:32.51,Karaoke,,0,0,0,,surechigau otona tachi wa tsubuyaku no sa
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.30,0:00:37.64,Karaoke,,0,0,0,,"ai toka yume toka risou mo wakaru kedo
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.85,0:00:43.81,Karaoke,,0,0,0,,me no mae no genjitsu wa sonna ni amaku nai" tte
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.94,0:00:50.15,Karaoke,,0,0,0,,tsumazuki nagara mo korogari nagara mo
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.94,0:00:55.36,Karaoke,,0,0,0,,kasabuta darake no jyounetsu wo wasuretaku nai
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.32,0:00:58.83,Karaoke,,0,0,0,,otona ni narenai bokura no
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.16,0:01:01.33,Karaoke,,0,0,0,,tsuyogari wo hitotsu kiite kure
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.25,0:01:04.54,Karaoke,,0,0,0,,nige mo kakure mo shinai kara
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.62,0:01:07.46,Karaoke,,0,0,0,,waraitai yatsu dake warae
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.71,0:01:10.25,Karaoke,,0,0,0,,semete tayori nai bokura no
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.46,0:01:12.80,Karaoke,,0,0,0,,jiyuu no me wo tsumitoranai de
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.42,0:01:15.80,Karaoke,,0,0,0,,mizu wo ageru sono yakume wo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.88,0:01:18.89,Karaoke,,0,0,0,,hataseba iindarou?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.25,0:00:26.21,KaraokeT,,0,0,0,,On the uphill road that leads to tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.55,0:00:32.51,KaraokeT,,0,0,0,,We pass by adults who tell us this
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.30,0:00:37.64,KaraokeT,,0,0,0,,"I can understand ideals such as love and dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.85,0:00:43.81,KaraokeT,,0,0,0,,but the real world isn't as easy as you think"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.94,0:00:50.15,KaraokeT,,0,0,0,,Even though we keep tripping and falling
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.94,0:00:55.36,KaraokeT,,0,0,0,,We have to remember these pains of growing up
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.32,0:00:58.83,KaraokeT,,0,0,0,,For all of us who can't force ourselves to do so yet
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.16,0:01:01.33,KaraokeT,,0,0,0,,Listen to this one thing I have to say
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.25,0:01:04.54,KaraokeT,,0,0,0,,I won't run or cower away
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.62,0:01:07.46,KaraokeT,,0,0,0,,So whoever wants to laugh at me, go ahead
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.71,0:01:10.25,KaraokeT,,0,0,0,,Since we can't be relied upon yet
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.46,0:01:12.80,KaraokeT,,0,0,0,,Don't take away our seed of freedom
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.42,0:01:15.80,KaraokeT,,0,0,0,,The task of nurturing this plant
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.88,0:01:18.89,KaraokeT,,0,0,0,,That's all we have to do, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.98,0:01:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{Intro}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.12,0:01:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Kiyomaro. Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.46,0:01:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's c...cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.09,0:01:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. I'll close it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.72,0:01:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.30,0:01:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,No wonder it's cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.80,0:02:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It snowed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.97,0:02:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Gash.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.52,0:02:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Normally when it snows...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.31,0:02:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Kiyomaro. It's snow!\NSnow has fallen.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.07,0:02:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's make a snowman together.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.07,0:02:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what you normally do...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.11,0:02:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you still upset about losing to Bali?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.16,0:02:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.54,0:02:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed, Bali was strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.83,0:02:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Like him,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.83,0:02:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,there are other demons\Nas strong as Brago.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.46,0:02:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.79,0:02:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what Brago and\NSherry are up to now?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.88,0:02:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{Part A}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.80,0:02:46.39,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\fs55\pos(488,420)}Snowfield Rumble!! A Regal Presence
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.20,0:03:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,My Lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.24,0:03:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's very dangerous to go that fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.29,0:03:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The monsters are nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.33,0:03:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's extremely dangerous\Nfor you, so stay put.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.21,0:03:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I cannot do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.30,0:03:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Jee!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.09,0:03:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I am alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.10,0:03:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave him. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.53,0:03:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Brago?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.95,0:03:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The demon's scent is weak.\NThey already left.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.87,0:03:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We lost them again?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.17,0:03:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's common these days, for them\Nto escape in the nick of time...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.22,0:04:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I was expecting a worthy challenger,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.18,0:04:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,but they cowered\Nand ran away.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.55,0:04:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,But... they made the right choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.43,0:04:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Those who fight me,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.18,0:04:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,only realize their weakness.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.74,0:04:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Brago, what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.83,0:04:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a demon, but I sense danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.90,0:05:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,How big...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.21,0:05:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.42,0:05:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,At this rate, they'll be killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.01,0:05:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeff... Grab the gun!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.43,0:05:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Quickly, get revenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.27,0:05:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Reisu!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.97,0:06:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandpa!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.97,0:06:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandpa! Are you alright?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.85,0:06:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The wounds are terrible.\NWe have to call for help.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.40,0:06:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Brago, give me a hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.24,0:06:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Jee. How are his wounds?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.49,0:06:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,For now, his bleeding has stopped,\Nbut he should see a doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.95,0:06:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I am fine now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.87,0:06:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a reason I\Ncannot leave this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.54,0:06:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.54,0:06:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't overdo it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.09,0:06:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,On another note,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.22,0:06:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,you said you wanted to get revenge?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.68,0:06:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Last year my daughter and her\Nhusband, this boy's parents,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.89,0:07:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,were bitten to death by that bear.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.44,0:07:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,That's terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.07,0:07:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why didn't you pick\Nup the gun and shoot it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.11,0:07:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Coward.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.12,0:07:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Brago! Stop that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.45,0:07:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you say that to a child!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.87,0:07:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate cowards.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.54,0:07:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.17,0:07:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you have any sympathy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.80,0:07:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.43,0:07:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going out for some exercise.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.43,0:07:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,If I stay here with you,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.26,0:07:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,my muscles will get stiff.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.43,0:07:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Go back to the hotel and get some rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.48,0:07:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.94,0:07:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,When did I say I needed to rest?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.27,0:07:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't say it as if I'm holding you back.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.53,0:07:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with his attitude?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.99,0:07:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,For once he should\Nexperience being powerless.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.45,0:07:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not it,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.70,0:08:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,he's concerned about your health.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.58,0:08:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.96,0:08:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Concerned about me...\Nhe didn't seem so!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.50,0:08:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,My Lady, you don't see that\NBrago-sama has changed quite a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.34,0:08:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,At first he was dangerous and violent,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.01,0:08:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,but now I see that he\Nhas become dignified.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.10,0:08:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Brago?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.27,0:08:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.27,0:08:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Strict and yet kind,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.77,0:08:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,the presence of a king.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.27,0:08:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Jee.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.28,0:08:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You're flattering him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.32,0:08:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not so.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.99,0:08:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,As you say,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.66,0:08:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,he seems to have lost\Nhis destructive nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.87,0:08:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of my way, old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.21,0:08:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't interfere!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.46,0:08:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I will not.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.25,0:08:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I will not allow you to hurt\NLady Sherry any further!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.17,0:08:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You dare say that, old man?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.92,0:08:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll finish you right this minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.26,0:08:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm alright, Jee.\NPlease stand back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.43,0:08:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But, my Lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.22,0:09:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen to me, Brago.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.89,0:09:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I was saying that we\Nshould go somewhere else.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.98,0:09:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,If we practice the spells here,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.40,0:09:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,we will involve people\Nunnecessarily. Therefore-
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.11,0:09:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop being a fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.57,0:09:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,If they're unnecessary\Nthen they don't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.40,0:09:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.70,0:09:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,As irritating as this sounds,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.70,0:09:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to team up with a human\Nweakling like yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.45,0:09:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if the demon is strong,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.33,0:09:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,a weak human will cause him to lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.21,0:09:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Throw away any\Nunnecessary thoughts!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.21,0:09:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Be ruthless and bring out everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.80,0:09:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Ignite your anger and hatred.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.97,0:09:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Then bring forth the\Npower from the book!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.43,0:09:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't... I'll tear him to pieces!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.48,0:09:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.02,0:09:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,you shall never become a king.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.19,0:09:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I am your one and only bookkeeper.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.95,0:09:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.20,0:10:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why you're trying to subdue me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.70,0:10:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,If I die you can no\Nlonger use your power.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.17,0:10:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You are just like her,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.21,0:10:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,the one who manipulated\NKoko's emotions, Zophise!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.68,0:10:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You only think of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.55,0:10:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone else is beneath you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.68,0:10:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Rather than obeying someone like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.27,0:10:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll slit my own throat!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.73,0:10:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,My... Lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.73,0:10:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,To you demons, I have\Nnothing but hatred.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.45,0:10:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, Brago.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.74,0:10:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want to become the King,\Nthen obey me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.20,0:10:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Or,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.16,0:10:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,would you rather not become king\Nbecause of your selfishness?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.87,0:10:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't ever think that you can manipulate\Nthe hearts of human beings!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.84,0:10:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't underestimate\Nhumans that much!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.59,0:11:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You do not have the right\Nto become the king!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.53,0:11:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You think I'd steal your dinner?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.25,0:11:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,In any case...\Nhelp me get some exercise.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.97,0:11:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{Part B}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.36,0:12:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you. I'm quite warm now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.53,0:12:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll have to head back\Nto the hotel before dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.03,0:12:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Please excuse us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.83,0:12:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm in your debt.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.91,0:12:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Please be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.79,0:12:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeff, I'm sorry about Brago.\NHe said mean things to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.64,0:12:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Brago.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.19,0:12:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Brago.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.19,0:12:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You defeated it for Jeff.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.78,0:12:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get me wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.07,0:12:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I came across it in the forest\Nso I took it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.24,0:12:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Brago-sama has changed quite a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.16,0:12:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Strict and yet kind,\Nthe presence of a king.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.75,0:12:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it good? You have\Navenged your parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.96,0:13:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Boy. Become stronger,\Nand never show your tears.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.72,0:13:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Crying will not get you anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.26,0:13:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Mind your own business.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.68,0:13:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Who asked you to do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.14,0:13:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I was going to get revenge\Nwith my own hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.48,0:13:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeff.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.98,0:13:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm terribly sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.86,0:13:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Deep inside he's relieved.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.65,0:13:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Not being honest about it,\Nsounds like someone we know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.99,0:13:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm heading back to the hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.30,0:13:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,For goodness sakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.72,0:13:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Sherry, good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.77,0:13:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.89,0:13:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,For once I was able to get\Na good night's sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.73,0:14:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.28,0:14:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is Brago?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.94,0:14:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Brago-sama has already awoken
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.53,0:14:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,and said he'll go out\Nfor some exercise,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.24,0:14:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,before we start off today.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.12,0:14:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,He's so self-centered.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.35,0:14:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Please stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.56,0:14:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever you say, we shall\Nnot leave this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.77,0:14:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.77,0:14:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're like that, we'll just bulldoze\Nyou along with the cottage.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.86,0:14:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Bro, there's someone coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.50,0:15:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Who the hell are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.29,0:15:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Brago-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.33,0:15:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,These are conning real-estate agents.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.09,0:15:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Boy. Become stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.13,0:15:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And never show your tears.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.05,0:15:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Crying will not get you anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.93,0:15:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Pray to become stronger,\Nand find the man's way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.69,0:15:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,This place belongs to me and\Nmy grandfather. Go away!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.11,0:15:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You sound so manly, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.41,0:15:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What if I say no?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.25,0:15:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I will... become stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.22,0:15:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,A man must not show tears!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.18,0:15:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,This kid's a nuisance. Hey, here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.61,0:16:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.83,0:16:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,A new spell?\NWhat does this mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.34,0:16:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Could something be\Nhappening to Brago?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.42,0:16:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.18,0:16:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.60,0:16:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeff...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.22,0:16:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,No more, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.60,0:16:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.56,0:16:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.57,0:16:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You dare interfere?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.16,0:16:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.45,0:17:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Bulldoze them down!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.25,0:17:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it really alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.59,0:17:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You should run. There's no\Npoint in getting involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.94,0:17:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You were saying "don't interfere"\Nand "bulldoze them".
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.94,0:17:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you saying that to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.24,0:17:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.16,0:17:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,This guy... what an\Noverwhelming presence he has.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.99,0:17:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, get out of my sight!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.50,0:17:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Excuse us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.46,0:17:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,But, bro. We can't back down like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.09,0:17:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.05,0:17:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Just in case,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.88,0:17:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I planted dynamite in the mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.19,0:18:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Get what you deserve, you bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.32,0:18:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay calm.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.37,0:18:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Dioga Gurabidon!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.28,0:18:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you know that I'd be here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.86,0:19:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,A new spell appeared,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.78,0:19:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,and so I thought\Nsomething was going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.12,0:19:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Brago-sama.\NThank you very much,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.42,0:19:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,for saving us from them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.01,0:19:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Brago, you... helped them?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.97,0:19:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't mistake me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.64,0:19:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to swat\Nsome noisy flies.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.72,0:19:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Big brother. I didn't run.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.98,0:19:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I will become a strong man.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.40,0:19:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.86,0:19:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll become much stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.73,0:19:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.11,0:19:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.90,0:19:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You can smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.28,0:19:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the first time I saw it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.32,0:19:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not smiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.49,0:19:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Brago.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.62,0:19:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Brago-sama has changed quite a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.67,0:19:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Strict and yet kind,\Nthe presence of a king.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.34,0:19:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.92,0:19:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Brago,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.09,0:20:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,if you like, we can stay for another day.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.55,0:20:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Be quiet. The demons\Nwill elude us again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.43,0:20:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.72,0:20:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so self-centered.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.97,0:20:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen to me for a...\NOh, see you, Jeff.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.14,0:20:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.44,0:20:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Good bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.27,0:20:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.78,0:20:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow. They've made something huge.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.66,0:20:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Takamine-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.08,0:20:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Suzume, Umagon and I made this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.91,0:20:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it great?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.08,0:20:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't get my\Npermission to build this!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.03,0:21:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{Ending}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.49,0:21:12.62,Karaoke,,0,0,0,,Stars atarashii mirai e to...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.46,0:21:17.46,Karaoke,,0,0,0,,akiramenai hitori janai
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.88,0:21:23.88,Karaoke,,0,0,0,,mou mayowanai yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.60,0:21:35.89,Karaoke,,0,0,0,,me no mae no genjitsu ni
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.40,0:21:40.90,Karaoke,,0,0,0,,he kon de shimau koto hoshi no kazu
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.23,0:21:44.78,Karaoke,,0,0,0,,yuugure no aka wo mita
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.07,0:21:49.78,Karaoke,,0,0,0,,boku ni hitsuyou na kawaranai yuuki
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.99,0:21:53.70,Karaoke,,0,0,0,,boku wa boku de kimi wa kimi no
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.08,0:21:57.83,Karaoke,,0,0,0,,yuzurenai jounetsu
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.42,0:22:04.59,Karaoke,,0,0,0,,me wo sorasazu ni tatakai tsuzukeru koto
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.26,0:22:08.22,Karaoke,,0,0,0,,We've gotta take the stars
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.51,0:22:14.68,Karaoke,,0,0,0,,sorezore no nido to nai toki wo kizamou
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.06,0:22:18.81,Karaoke,,0,0,0,,shinjitsu wa Rhythm Nation
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.15,0:22:25.61,Karaoke,,0,0,0,,toki no nagare ni makenaide arukou
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.94,0:22:30.82,Karaoke,,0,0,0,,You don't have to worry about tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.49,0:21:12.62,KaraokeT,,0,0,0,,Stars, to the new tomorrow...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.46,0:21:17.46,KaraokeT,,0,0,0,,don't give up, you are not alone
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.88,0:21:23.88,KaraokeT,,0,0,0,,I have no more doubts, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.60,0:21:35.89,KaraokeT,,0,0,0,,to the truth before my eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.40,0:21:40.90,KaraokeT,,0,0,0,,to the things I give in to, the number of stars
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.23,0:21:44.78,KaraokeT,,0,0,0,,I saw the redness of evening
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.07,0:21:49.78,KaraokeT,,0,0,0,,the unchanging courage that I need
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.99,0:21:53.70,KaraokeT,,0,0,0,,me and mine, you and yours
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.08,0:21:57.83,KaraokeT,,0,0,0,,unyielding passion
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.42,0:22:04.59,KaraokeT,,0,0,0,,don't turn your eyes away, continue to fight
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.26,0:22:08.22,KaraokeT,,0,0,0,,We've gotta take the stars
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.51,0:22:14.68,KaraokeT,,0,0,0,,try to carve the moments that won't come again
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.06,0:22:18.81,KaraokeT,,0,0,0,,truth is Rhythm Nation
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.15,0:22:25.61,KaraokeT,,0,0,0,,don't lose to the flow of time, walk...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.94,0:22:30.82,KaraokeT,,0,0,0,,You don't have to worry about tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.04,0:22:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{Preview}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.08,0:22:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Kiyomaro, what is this exactly?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.21,0:22:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The words on this look\Nsimilar to our book.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.59,0:22:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.59,0:22:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I've seen this tablet before.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.09,0:22:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Right! Using our open minded thinking\Nwe'll experiment on this tablet.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.30,0:22:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. I'm going to train with Tio.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.80,0:22:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time on Konjiki no Gash Bell:
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.81,0:22:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,A Wicked Thief!\NThe Mystery of the Tablet.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.39,0:22:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What I must do to make Gash the king?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.14,0:23:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The key is in this tablet!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.06,0:23:03.98,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\fs60\bord3\pos(488,465)}A Wicked Thief!\NThe Mystery of the Tablet

